OL,3,CEast Midlands to get a Mayor after
OL,4,Ccouncils vote for #4 billion
OL,5,Cdevolution deal
OL,7,FResidents across the East Midlands
OL,8,Fwill get the chance to vote for the
OL,9,Ffirst-ever East Midlands Mayor next
OL,10,FMay, after councils gave the go-ahead
OL,11,Fto devolution for the region.
OL,13,FToday (Thursday 7 December),
OL,14,FDerbyshire County Council,
OL,15,FNottinghamshire County Council, Derby
OL,16,FCity Council and Nottingham City
OL,17,FCouncil each approved plans to create
OL,18,Fthe East Midlands Combined County
OL,19,FAuthority (EMCCA), which will come
OL,20,Finto existence next Spring.
